descriptionHtml:
My first Mod. A little, fullspeaken Quest with a new, very dark dungeon. 
It beginns at the Honey Brewery in Whiterun.

In this quest you must bring a walking stick of an old man back. It is in a very dark dungeon, where you need a lightsource.

Workshop ( http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=10997)

Auch in deutsch (Also in German) (http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=10605)
